title: Tyler Johnson with PA & Charch
description: Tyler Johnson has gone from his amazing Gophers career, right into Super Bowl history in his rookie season as he and his Bucs hoisted the Lombardi trophy last weekend. Tyler and his agent, Blake Baratz, stop by for a couple segments on the feast!
